description: A road is closed following a collision between a car and a motorbike, Surrey Police say.
title: Man in hospital after Guildford crash
title_page: Man in hospital after Guildford crash - BBC News
maintext:
A man has been taken to hospital by air ambulance after two vehicles crashed near Guildford.
Surrey Police said Salt Box Road, between the A320 and A322 Worplesdon Road, was closed on Monday morning, following a collision between a car and a motorbike.
Officers attended the scene with paramedics after being called shortly after 07:50 GMT.
Surrey Police has urged people to avoid the area.
